                    <p class="last-updated">Last updated: January 2025</p>
                    
                    <div class="legal-text">
                        <h2>1. Refund Eligibility</h2>
                        <p>We want you to be completely satisfied with our services. If you are not satisfied with your purchase, you may be eligible for a refund under the conditions outlined below.</p>
                        
                        <h2>2. Full Refund Conditions</h2>
                        <p>You are eligible for a full refund if:</p>
                        <ul>
                            <li>You request a refund within 7 days of your initial purchase</li>
                            <li>You have attended fewer than 2 lessons</li>
                            <li>There are technical issues on our end that prevent lesson delivery</li>
                        </ul>
                        
                        <h2>3. Partial Refund Conditions</h2>
                        <p>Partial refunds may be available for unused lessons in your package, calculated on a pro-rata basis, if:</p>
                        <ul>
                            <li>You have completed less than 50% of your purchased lessons</li>
                            <li>You provide at least 48 hours notice before cancellation</li>
                        </ul>
                        
                        <h2>4. Non-Refundable Situations</h2>
                        <p>Refunds will not be provided in the following cases:</p>
                        <ul>
                            <li>More than 50% of purchased lessons have been completed</li>
                            <li>Refund request is made more than 30 days after purchase</li>
                            <li>Cancellation due to student's unavailability or scheduling conflicts</li>
                        </ul>
                        
                        <h2>5. Refund Process</h2>
                        <p>To request a refund:</p>
                        <ol>
                            <li>Contact us at admin@clearn.top with your refund request</li>
                            <li>Provide your order details and reason for refund</li>
                            <li>We will review your request within 3-5 business days</li>
                            <li>Approved refunds will be processed within 7-10 business days</li>
                        </ol>
                        
                        <h2>6. Payment Method</h2>
                        <p>Refunds will be issued to the original payment method used for the purchase. Processing times may vary depending on your payment provider.</p>
                        
                        <h2>7. Contact Us</h2>
                        <p>If you have any questions about our refund policy or need to request a refund, please contact us at admin@clearn.top</p>
